![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d71ee072-c824-46d1-8983-113cbccce8ee/20240513_170853.jpg?format=original)

Raw opens with Jey Uso vs Ilja Dragunov being announced as the main event of tonight’s show.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/456a6886-ee50-4aca-a884-1c18b7b29817/20240513_170846.jpg?format=original)

Drew McIntyre comes out and says he’s done with chasing CM Punk for now. He wants Damien Priest and the world championship. Priest comes out. Drew calls him more of a man then Punk for stepping up.

Priest tells Drew to look in the mirror. He says he wanted to have a World Championship banger with Drew McIntyre at WrestleMania but Drew wouldn’t let him cash in.

McIntyre is the one who said out loud in a promo that if Priest was smart, he would wait for McIntyre to take out Rollins then cash in. So he did.

This is all Drew's fault but if he wants a World Title shot. Drew's got one.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/75a7e3db-0424-4aa5-96ed-951005e0206e/20240513_171813.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c60bcdca-ad07-4e06-b528-da46cdf9ded7/20240513_171808.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_QUEEN OF THE RING ROUND 2: IYO SKY DEF SHAYNA BASZLER_**
    

Pretty fun match. Straight up. No interference. Nice change of pace.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2ba6386e-a42b-410e-ade5-0c2ca7e30091/Screenshot_20240513_174358.jpg?format=original)

Lilian Garcia is here!!!!!! She tells Samantha Irvin that she's doing a great job and she's so proud. They embrace.

Lilian introduces the next match, Kofi Kingston vs Gunther

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/14608000-ccff-48ac-8109-cf582b4d2df8/Screenshot_20240513_174414.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/764adaef-dab8-44d7-8316-ce87b61f8508/Screenshot_20240513_180729.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_KING OF THE RING ROUND 2: GUNTHER DEF KOFI KINGSTON_**
    

Gunther is hands down my favorite WWE Wrestler. He brings my favorite style of wrestling to a place it really doesn't belong and its interesting seeing him drag wrestlers into his match.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/fec34ceb-08e3-4dc2-b0d9-2a299584f1b3/Screenshot_20240513_180736.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7ff0459c-1f3a-48b2-85a2-a558cc4658cd/Screenshot_20240513_181047.jpg?format=original)

Liv Morgan asks Lyra Valkyria was Becky Lynch always such a bitch? She turns around and gets slapped by Becky. Liv smiles as Becky walks away.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/fe1e24ad-bbab-4fb1-bce1-9c943dfdaebb/20240513_181858.jpg?format=original)

Kofi Kingston runs into Karrion Kross backstage. A possible confrontation down the line.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/bab7bd55-3c5d-426f-a3f4-1c06bc0111c6/Screenshot_20240513_181917.jpg?format=original)

*   ## _BRONSON REED DEF. TOZAWA_
    

A squash match where Bronson Reed destroyed Tozawa while Chad Gable berates him the entire time.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/97eabde4-ce1b-4f51-85bc-a308ffb47fa7/Screenshot_20240513-184044_Chrome.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_QUEEN OF THE RING ROUND TWO: LYRA VALKYRIA DEF. ZOEY STARKS_**
    

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ebf9a41e-a08c-4853-9bc9-dc7f46e6c05f/Screenshot_20240513_185225.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_SAMI ZAYN DEF. OTIS_**
    

Chad Gable basically cost Otis this match by chastising him for doing the worm. Gable keeps berating Otis after the match until Sami runs in to beat on him.

Gable blames Otis for Sami's attack and slaps him across the face.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/cc74cc5e-bf95-4b21-83a4-712255d4eb4b/Screenshot_20240513_191326.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_BECKY LYNCH DEF. DAKOTA KAI BY DQ_**
    

Damage CTRL jumps Becky before Dakota could tap to the DisArmHer. Lyra saves Becky again. But not before Liv Morgan takes Becky out anyway.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1d642d52-7a1c-4576-9a82-b38be08b9ef9/Screenshot_20240513_191638.jpg?format=original)

Ilja Dragunov is cutting a promo about how he’s a different kind of beast because he has actually beaten Gunther before. And then Gunther appears. He stares down Ilja, smiles. Then walks off.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c7c69fcd-ce6a-4a06-962c-295329292385/Screenshot_20240513_193636.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_NUMBER 1 CONTENDERS FOR THE WORLD TAG TEAM CHAMPIONSHIPS: JUDGEMENT DAY DEF. NEW CATCH REPUBLIC, CREED BROS AND AUTHORS OF PAIN_**
    

Carlito continues to prove himself worthy to Judgement Day by helping them come out on top here.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/57631342-e7e6-4891-adf7-ac7ea0a951af/Screenshot_20240513_193642.jpg?format=original)

